you to do tomorrow.

20:11.480 --> 20:12.720
Whatever you want.

20:12.760 --> 20:14.960
♪

20:15.000 --> 20:18.240
You know, it's Jamie's
month's mind mass tomorrow.

20:18.280 --> 20:22.200
Yeah.

20:22.240 --> 20:27.040
