20:37.720 --> 20:39.880
Look, you need
to go to bed.

20:39.920 --> 20:41.400
When are you coming
home, Daddy?

20:41.440 --> 20:43.880
I'll be home tomorrow
for your birthday party.

20:43.920 --> 20:45.240
It's going to be
a great party.

20:45.280 --> 20:47.560
Yeah. That's why
I'm going to be there.

20:47.600 --> 20:48.680
"Buenos naches."

20:48.720 --> 20:49.920
"Buenos naches."

20:49.960 --> 20:55.560
♪

20:55.600 --> 20:57.680
Did Con pay you
for Fudge?

20:57.720 --> 21:00.440
Yeah.
Thanks.

21:00.480 --> 21:02.720
I want you
to set up one
of the Kinsellas.

21:02.760 --> 21:04.440
We will.

21:04.480 --> 21:06.760
I want Michael.

21:06.800 --> 21:08.720
I'm working on it.

21:08.760 --> 21:10.120
He's real careful,
you know?

21:10.160 --> 21:12.120
Doesn't trust anyone.

21:12.160 --> 21:15.320
I want one
of the family.

21:15.360 --> 21:18.680
We know,
and I'll get one for you.

21:18.720 --> 21:20.520
Might have a lead
on one of them tomorrow

21:20.560 --> 21:21.720
and I'll let Con know.

21:21.760 --> 21:23.320
You just make sure
you do.

21:23.360 --> 21:26.200
♪

21:26.240 --> 21:27.280
We will.

21:27.320 --> 21:30.600
♪

21:30.640 --> 21:31.760
Alright, Kem.

