Heya.

24:27.560 --> 24:30.440
♪

24:30.480 --> 24:33.400
If you don't want
to do it,

24:33.440 --> 24:34.720
it's okay.

24:34.760 --> 24:37.600
♪

24:37.640 --> 24:40.000
No.

24:40.040 --> 24:41.160
I do.

