♪

24:44.320 --> 24:45.200
Good.

24:45.240 --> 24:48.480
♪

24:48.520 --> 24:50.480
See ya later.

24:50.520 --> 24:51.560
Yeah.

24:51.600 --> 24:54.440
♪

