[Locks click]

25:02.120 --> 25:05.160
♪

25:05.200 --> 25:08.120
[Clank, whirring]

25:08.160 --> 25:10.040
♪

25:10.080 --> 25:12.240
Good luck with your
little fucking powwow.

25:12.280 --> 25:14.680
I'm just trying to protect
this family, Frank.

25:14.720 --> 25:16.120
Enjoy your moment.

25:16.160 --> 25:17.920
'Cause, as soon
as this is over,

25:17.960 --> 25:20.080
I'm going to put you right
back in your fuckin' box.

25:20.120 --> 25:25.320
♪

25:25.360 --> 25:27.000
[Seatbelt whirs, clicks]

25:27.040 --> 25:29.880
