in memory of Jamie Kinsella.

37:23.200 --> 37:26.240
The grace
of our Lord Jesus Christ

37:26.280 --> 37:28.160
and the love of God

37:28.200 --> 37:30.400
and the communion
of the Holy Spirit

37:30.440 --> 37:31.760
