And with your spirit.

37:33.400 --> 37:36.680
[Engines whining]

37:36.720 --> 37:40.400
♪

37:40.440 --> 37:42.760
I'll...call him.

37:42.800 --> 37:47.960
I'll see
wh-what he will accept.

37:48.000 --> 37:50.960
Whatever it is,
we'll get it.

37:51.000 --> 38:00.640
