38:08.400 --> 38:18.320
♪

38:18.360 --> 38:22.960
♪

38:23.000 --> 38:24.880
So, what you got
for me?

38:24.920 --> 38:28.080
Scriven:
Let us acknowledge
our sins.

38:28.120 --> 38:31.440
I confess to almighty God,

38:31.480 --> 38:33.960
and to you,
my brothers and sisters,

38:34.000 --> 38:37.480
that I have sinned,
in my thoughts and in my words,

38:37.520 --> 38:41.480
in what I have done
and what I have failed to do,

38:41.520 --> 38:44.520
through my fault,
through my fault,

38:44.560 --> 38:47.080
through my grievous fault;

